overview: School Principal Vaughn uses reluctant teacher Mr. O'Neil who owes her a certain debt to lure a student named Rebecca into sex trap. Compromising O'Neil's principles was even easier than Vaughn thought it would be.  The coach of a football team prepares a young star athlete named Jesse to become a sex object at the behest of his lover Catherine , who is the co-owner of the team. She succeeds in setting up a ploy to get what she wants and he'll have to give in and satisfy her every command
title: Compromised Principles
